/tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">17PC BACKPACK TOY BUNDLE - Officially licensed Marvel Avengers backpack bundle comes with 17 toys and school supplies for boys: an activity play pack, a spiral notebook with pen, erasers, and a kawaii- style backpack; All accessories are safe for children ages 3 and up with adult supervision</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DRAWSTRING CINCH BAG - Easy-to-use cinch closure ensures school supplies and accessories stay secured; Adjustable drawstring cinch provides custom size and comfort; Measures 18” x 13”; Water-resistant polyester material</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ACTIVITY PLAY PACK - 6pc Avengers play pack comes with a 24 page coloring and activity book with a cool sticker sheet and 4 colors; Encourages creativity and imagination; Great for occupying children during long road trips</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPIRAL NOTEBOOK - Avengers-themed spiral notebook comes with a matching clip top ballpoint pen; Kids can practice their penmanship, take notes, and doodle; Spiral style notebook can also double as a diary or journal</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ERASER SET - 8pc set comes with 8 different shaped erasers kids can use to correct mistakes on homework and school assignments; Small size will fit inside most pencil cases and school supplies organizers</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Marvel Avengers 16pc Cinch Bag Drawstring Backpacks Erasers Play Pack Gift Bundle Boys Age 3 and Up</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">39.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Unleash the hero within this holiday season with the ultimate Avengers-Themed Gift Set! Perfect for young fans, this action-packed set includes everything they need to show off their Avengers spirit while staying organized.</p><p>What's inside?</p><p>The 18” by 13” drawstring bag is perfect for school supplies, sporting gear, and more. With a secure cinch closure, your little hero can carry everything they need safely and easily!</p><p>The adjustable straps ensure a perfect, comfortable fit for any young Avenger ready to tackle the day with ease.</p><p>These colorful Avengers-themed erasers add a fun pop to every pencil case. Perfectly sized for school bags and on-the-go adventures.</p><p>Featuring coloring pages, puzzles, stickers, and crayons, this activity book fuels creativity while inspiring hours of entertainment. Plus, the perforated pages let kids proudly display their masterpiece creations!\n</p><div><br></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2025</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t&nbsp;<table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <br>",
